Class ExpandEmbedding

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple
      • org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple3<Embedding,GradoopId[],GradoopId>
        • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.single.cypher.operators.expand.tuples.ExpandEmbedding
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ExpandEmbedding
extends org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple3<Embedding,GradoopId[],GradoopId>
    Represents an intermediate result for the expand operator. The base part (f0) is the immutable input generated by previous operations. The path (f1) is the path we grow while expanding. The end node (f2) is the last element in expanded path (a node). It is stored separately to enable using it as a join column.
